		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Adam Fisher</strong></span> writes, &ldquo;As a person who writes, I am both a liar and a thief. So you can say I&rsquo;m a liar and a thief in New York City. Or, I paint apartments in New York City. Please don&rsquo;t say I&rsquo;m a lying, thieving housepainter. I like to maintain a fantasy of integrity when it comes to housepainting.&rdquo;</p><a href="/contributors/adam-fisher" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
